## `OrthographicCamera` (`OrthographicCamera.h`)

Stores three matrices: projection, view, and combined view-projection. Constructed with `(left, right, bottom, top)` bounds using a near/far of `(-1, 1)`. `SetPosition` and `SetRotation` trigger `RecalculateViewMatrix`.

`OrthographicCameraComponent` is the ECS wrapper that holds a `pg::OrthographicCamera` value.

