## Data Flow per Frame

```
Other systems emit DrawXxxInFrameEvent components onto entities
          |
          v
Renderer2DSystem::Update()
  reads OrthographicCameraComponent → extracts ViewProjection matrix
  reads ResourceMapSingletonComponent → texture/shader/font maps
  reads EngineConfigSingletonComponent → default shader UUIDs
          |
          v
  [if first frame] Init()
    VertexBuffer::Create(empty, BATCH_MAX_COUNT * VERTEX_STRIDE)  → Dx11VertexBuffer (DYNAMIC)
    IndexBuffer::Create(empty, BATCH_MAX_COUNT * QUAD_INDEX_COUNT) → Dx11IndexBuffer (DYNAMIC)
    resolves m_QuadShader and m_TextShader from ResourceMapSingletonComponent
          |
          v
  Render()
    Clear() → ClearRenderTargetView(0.3, 0.3, 0.3, 1.0)
    BeginScene()
      RenderCommand::Begin()
        [deferred resize if needed: CleanupRenderTarget → ResizeBuffers → CreateRenderTarget]
        OMSetRenderTargets, Clear, RSSetViewports
      IASetVertexBuffers, IASetIndexBuffer
      PSSetShaderResources(0, defaultTexture), PSSetSamplers
      Dx11Shader::Bind() → IASetInputLayout, VSSetShader, PSSetShader
      UploadUniformMat4("u_ViewProjection") → Dx11ConstantBuffer<XMMATRIX> → VSSetConstantBuffers(0)
          |
          v
    ProcessRenderRequests()
      foreach DrawQuadInFrameEvent / DrawUIQuadInFrameEvent
        → DrawLayerBatch() → appends QuadData into m_LayerBatchMap[layer][textureID]
      foreach DrawSpriteInFrameEvent
        → DrawSprite() → DrawLayerBatch()
      foreach DrawStringInFrameEvent / DrawUIStringInFrameEvent
        → DrawString() → per-char DrawLayerBatch() into font atlas batch
          |
          v
    EndScene()
      Flush()
        foreach batch in m_BatchMap (texture-keyed, layerless):
          Bind texture, bind shader, SetVertices (WRITE_DISCARD), SetIndices (WRITE_DISCARD)
          DrawIndexed(indexCount)
        foreach layer 0..99:
          foreach batch in m_LayerBatchMap[layer]:
            Bind texture, bind shader, SetVertices, SetIndices, DrawIndexed
        clear both maps
      RenderCommand::End() → assert initialized
      Unbind VertexBuffer, Unbind IndexBuffer
```

